A dog that was found in a frozen lake has been reunited with its owners after they saw news coverage of his Coast Guard rescue.

Owner Jodi Benchich said that her 14-year-old dog KC went missing 10 days ago and she had been searching for him.

'(I) found that the rope was broke and I just dropped everything and went searching,' Ms Benchich told WXYZ.

